{"parentUuid":"a5aa2242-7c05-4905-9814-7205cdaf6cfb","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\0000250059\\AppData\\Roaming\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Start Menu\\Programs\\startup","sessionId":"e98fc7c9-5b86-4dde-ac74-4a64fb976dfa","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"ancient-wibbling-mochi","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01L7f2FZ1rvumv94zb8CozVN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"qutebrowser は QtWebEngine ベースのため、Chrome/Firefox 拡張機能（uBlock Origin）を直接インストールできません。\n\n## 代替手段\n\n### 1. Brave の広告ブロッカーを利用（不可）\nqutebrowser には組み込みの広告ブロッカーがあります。\n\n### 2. qutebrowser 内蔵の広告ブロッカー\n\n`config.py` に以下を追加:\n\n```python\nc.content.blocking.method = \"both\"  # \"adblock\" or \"hosts\" or \"both\"\n\nc.content.blocking.adblock.lists = [\n    \"https://easylist.to/easylist/easylist.txt\",\n    \"https://easylist.to/easylist/easyprivacy.txt\",\n    \"https://easylist-downloads.adblockplus.org/abp-filters-anti-cv.txt\",\n    \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/uBlockOrigin/uAssets/master/filters/filters.txt\",\n    \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/uBlockOrigin/uAssets/master/filters/annoyances.txt\",\n]\n```\n\nその後、qutebrowser 内で `:adblock-update` を実行してリストを更新。\n\n### 3. `method` の違い\n\n| method | 説明 |\n|--------|------|\n| `hosts` | ドメイン単位でブロック（軽量） |\n| `adblock` | Brave の adblock ライブラリ使用（要 `python-adblock`） |\n| `both` | 両方併用（最も効果的） |\n\n### 4. python-adblock のインストール\n\n`adblock` メソッドを使うには:\n\n```bash\npip install adblock\n```\n\n---\n\n**結論**: uBlock Origin そのものは使えませんが、`c.content.blocking.method = \"both\"` + uBlock Origin のフィルターリストを指定することで、近い効果が得られます。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":25332,"cache_read_input_tokens":7804,"output_tokens":619,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":25332,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","ite